sourcesContent:
import React from 'react';
import { Link as RouterLink } from 'react-router-dom';
import {
  Box,
  Container,
  Grid,
  Typography,
  Link,
  IconButton,
  useTheme,
} from '@mui/material';
import LinkedInIcon from '@mui/icons-material/LinkedIn';
import TwitterIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Twitter';
import FacebookIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Facebook';
import EmailIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Email';

function Footer() {
  const theme = useTheme();

  return (
    <Box
      component="footer"
      sx={{
        bgcolor: 'secondary.main',
        color: 'white',
        py: 6,
        mt: 'auto',
      }}
    >
      <Container maxWidth="lg">
        <Grid container spacing={4}>
          {/* Company Info */}
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
              MyConstructionCyberRisk
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
              Empowering construction projects with advanced cybersecurity solutions
              and risk management tools.
            </Typography>
            <Box sx={{ mt: 2 }}>
              <IconButton color="inherit" aria-label="LinkedIn">
                <LinkedInIcon />
              </IconButton>
              <IconButton color="inherit" aria-label="Twitter">
                <TwitterIcon />
              </IconButton>
              <IconButton color="inherit" aria-label="Facebook">
                <FacebookIcon />
              </IconButton>
              <IconButton color="inherit" aria-label="Email">
                <EmailIcon />
              </IconButton>
            </Box>
          </Grid>

          {/* Quick Links */}
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
              Quick Links
            </Typography>
            <Link
              component={RouterLink}
              to="/topic-modeling"
              color="inherit"
              display="block"
              sx={{ mb: 1 }}
            >
              Topic Modeling
            </Link>
            <Link
              component={RouterLink}
              to="/risk-identification"
              color="inherit"
              display="block"
              sx={{ mb: 1 }}
            >
              Risk Identification
            </Link>
            <Link
              component={RouterLink}
              to="/risk-quantification"
              color="inherit"
              display="block"
              sx={{ mb: 1 }}
            >
              Risk Quantification
            </Link>
            <Link
              component={RouterLink}
              to="/reports"
              color="inherit"
              display="block"
              sx={{ mb: 1 }}
            >
              Reports
            </Link>
          </Grid>

          {/* Contact Info */}
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
              Contact Us
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ mb: 1 }}>
              Email: info@constructioncyberrisk.com
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ mb: 1 }}>
              Phone: +1 (555) 123-4567
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2">
              Address: 123 Security Street, Cyber City, CS 12345
            </Typography>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>

        {/* Copyright */}
        <Box
          sx={{
            mt: 5,
            pt: 3,
            borderTop: 1,
            borderColor: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1)',
            textAlign: 'center',
          }}
        >
          <Typography variant="body2">
            Â© {new Date().getFullYear()} MyConstructionCyberRisk. All rights
            reserved.
          </Typography>
        </Box>
      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
}

export default Footer;
